title: Volunteer/Intern Interview
Application Type: The process took 3 weeks. I interviewed at A21 (CA)
Interview Descriptions: There was a set of two three interviews, the process took about three weeks - very laid back, largely questions about your qualifications and why you want to work there, as well as expectations for the internship, but you still want to dress appropriately (business casual or formal) and respond professionally.
Interview Questions: Why do you want to be a volunteer intern at A21?
